<template>
	
</template>
<script>
import { mapState, mapActions } from 'vuex';

export default {
	data() {
	  return {
	    email: '',
	    password: ''
	  }
	},
	computed: {
	  ...mapState([
	    'loggingIn',
	    'loginError',
	    'loginSuccessful'
	  ])
	},
	methods: {
	  ...mapActions([
	    'doLogin'
	  ]),
	  loginSubmit() {
	    this.doLogin({
	      email: this.email,
	      password: this.password
	    })
	  }
	}
}
</script>
<style scoped>
	
</style>
